latestPosts.caption:
Happy Birthday to 2 of my favorite girls 🤍 @pragyakapoor_ @billymanik81 

We grew up thinking real friendships only happened in school corridors, college canteens, and late-night hostel chats.

And while those are special, here’s the truth, some of the deepest bonds are still waiting to be formed.
In your adulthood, in your conference rooms. Sometimes at house parties. Or over fries and a 2 a.m. heart-to-heart you didn’t see coming.

It’s never too late to find your people. You just have to stay open.

latestPosts.caption:
A night I’ll hold close for a long time 🫶 @zeecineawards 

It was an incredible honor to pay homage to the women who’ve shaped the soul of Indian cinema. Their stories, their power, their grace… they’ve paved the way for so many generations. Performing to their iconic songs at the 23rd Zee Cine Awards was my little way of honoring everything they’ve given and still continue to give to the industry. 

Lucky to work with the best teams and a big thank you to @manishmalhotra05 , love how he always enhances and channels the personality of the artist through every occasion , definitely one of the favourite red carpets of myself in a long time.
